ome.smuggler.core.msg

Interface MessageSource<M,D>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChannelSource<ChannelMessage<M,D>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SchedulingSource<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CountedScheduleTask, EnqueueTask, ScheduleTask, SourceQueue

    public interface MessageSource<M,D>
extends ChannelSource<ChannelMessage<M,D>>
    Encapsulates the sending of an asynchronous message along a channel that supports metadata. This channel source imposes a minimal structure to the data being sent over the channel, namely that of a message containing data meant to be consumed by the receiving end and optionally metadata, typically used to configure the sending of the message.
    See Also:
    ChannelMessage, MessageSink
